snippet.title: Wonder Woman/Diana Saves Mera's Life - Gal Gadot & Amber Heard | Woman Saves Woman
snippet.description:
Wonder Woman/Diana Saves Mera's Life. Gal Gadot and Amber Heard. Diana Loves Mera. A Woman Saves a Woman's Life... "I cannot stand by while women's lives are lost." - Diana Prince.
We should see this happen on the Live screen TODAY!! Progress! 
#WonderWoman #GalGadot #AmberHeard #Mera #Aquaman #WomensRights 

- Since they're for Women's Rights and Equality, shouldn't we see this more often??
- A follower of Amber Heard uploaded this onto a social media site. 
🧡 Script said innocent lives, but we hear Women's Lives... 

#Romance #Action #Superheroes #Heroes #DianaPrince #Rescue #LGBTQ #funny #GenerationEquality #Music #SaveLives #SaveHer
